    "2 What to eat after breast cancer chemotherapy to recover quickly?",
    "Pay attention to a balanced diet during the recovery period, and eat more foods rich in protein, vitamins and minerals, such as fish, lean meat, beans, vegetables and fruits.",
    "At the same time, avoid eating spicy and stimulating foods and greasy foods.",
    "After breast cancer chemotherapy, you can eat foods high in protein, vitamins, and trace elements to accelerate wound healing.",
    "At the same time, avoid foods containing carcinogens, foods containing estrogen and growth hormones, and high-fat diets."
  ]
}